snippet.title: Mega Man: Super Fighting Robot - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Whoa, 5k views in the first day?! That's kinda awesome. Thanks for watching!

Update: Um. 20k? Holy crap. I am amazed.

A brand new Mega Man game is coming! Get your weapons ready!
Fight, shoot, and blast your way through 14 levels and save the world, once again.

Mega Man: Super Fighting Robot will be released Fall of 2015.

This is a non-profit fan-based game. Mega Man and all related characters are owned by Capcom.

Check out the Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Mega-Man-Super-Fighting-Robot/402614193259545
